lead_paragraph: Jimmy Walker birdied the last for a one-shot lead over Jason Day after Sunday's completion of the weather-interrupted third round of the PGA Championship at Baltusrol, where the final round was already underway.

headline.print_headline: Walker Leads Day by One Going Into Final Round of PGA
